name: THE RE-ENCHANTMENT OF THE WORLD 🌠
description: What happened to magic in the world? Was it replaced by calculus and utilitaristic rationality? We think so but our bet is that we can still bring it back. And this is going to happen only through our machines. There's magic in machines, enough magic to re-enchant the world. With this series of artworks, generated with different Notebooks, we want to represent the electric, psychedelic power that our tools and devices can express. Support this and you will also support the research of the entire project REINCANTAMENTO, available at this link: https://reincantamento.xyz.
